WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.018
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:00:06.019 --> 00:00:08.808
Good evening, family. Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:08.809 --> 00:00:17.177
I got around a little later because we went to church, and I was rushing to feed the kids and stuff before, and I apologize.

00:00:17.178 --> 00:00:21.128
I want to get on here earlier because there are so many of you that say, "Hey, I go to bed.

00:00:21.129 --> 00:00:24.538
What? You're praying way too late, Brandon."And I would love it.

00:00:24.539 --> 00:00:31.668
I think I'm trying to start to get the live streams around 7:00, but that'll affect going to Wednesday night church and stuff.

00:00:31.669 --> 00:00:42.208
I don't know what we're going to do. But I know in my heart when I do the live streams around 7:00, we'll get over 10,000 people on a live stream at one time.

00:00:42.209 --> 00:00:46.858
And so, I believe that's significant for prayer results. You know, we're touching the nations.

00:00:46.859 --> 00:00:46.958
I believe with all my heart we're touching the nations for Jesus.

00:00:46.959 --> 00:00:47.058
And people are getting saved, and it's just wonderful what God is doing here.

00:00:47.059 --> 00:00:47.158
So, I just want to be encouraging tonight about some of the things that the Lord was—we were praying over last night.

00:00:47.159 --> 00:00:47.258
Whenever the spirit of the Lord hit my little girl in that river as she was interceding for me, interceding with Diana, and they were praying, everybody kept saying, "I hear a third voice."We don't know who the third voice was.

00:00:47.259 --> 00:00:54.292
I kept thinking it was Sister Billie. I told Diana I thought she was playing something and they were praying alongside it, but there was nobody else in the house.

00:00:54.293 --> 00:01:05.118
They were in the closet and they were praying, and it was so loud in the closet that it sounded like a third person was praying with them, but there was not a third person.

00:01:05.119 --> 00:01:13.188
So, I thought it was really interesting because I even personally thought there was a third person.

00:01:13.189 --> 00:01:21.673
And I kept thinking, and I told Diana, I said, "That sounds familiar. Who is that?"And I was trying to figure it out myself.

00:01:21.674 --> 00:01:28.831
Diana said, "There was nobody in the closet with us."So, we tried to think about that.

00:01:28.832 --> 00:01:35.954
We thought about that all the rest of the night. Who was the third voice praying and interceding?

00:01:35.955 --> 00:01:43.222
It was loud. But it was interesting because so many of you heard the third voice, too. And Paisley was praying.

00:01:43.223 --> 00:01:53.125
What we were praying about, we saw great revival coming to the nation, but it was with the youth.

00:01:53.126 --> 00:02:10.893
I saw a stirring in the youth that was all over Australia, all over America, Europe, but God was touching the young people in a glorious way.

00:02:10.894 --> 00:02:18.390
In a glorious way that was over the top of anything I could dare ask or think concerning the youth.

00:02:18.391 --> 00:02:37.776
The Lord said, "The devil has come after the youth hard, but I'm coming after him harder."Brandon, there will be—and I saw at the Church of His Presence, I saw a major youth revival also taking place with the glorious outpouring that's going to take place there.

00:02:37.778 --> 00:02:52.603
And then that was the same thing the Lord was talking to us about the youth building that the church in Collinsville is building and what God is going to do with the outpouring of the spirit on the youth in Oklahoma.

00:02:52.604 --> 00:03:12.185
I know in my heart, just as Paisley was praying and interceding for the youth and for me—I mean for the broadcast—it was just over the top because she was in that travail, as you know.

00:03:12.186 --> 00:03:15.592
And everybody asks, "How old is Paisley?"I don't let Paisley come on the internet.

00:03:15.593 --> 00:03:24.238
She's my youngest, and she is just—she's not even a teenager yet; she's just a child.

00:03:24.239 --> 00:03:32.798
And so, most people want to know—no, I've got a lot of creepy people that follow me, and I protect Paisley.

00:03:32.799 --> 00:03:43.037
There's a call on Paisley's life, and even with my other children as we all know, but Paisley is already seeing, and so we just don't talk about it.

00:03:43.038 --> 00:03:48.555
God's developing some things inside her, and it's through prayer.

00:03:48.556 --> 00:04:02.345
I teach her everything I know; we pray in the car together, and I'm teaching her even before she becomes a teenager how to jump in these rivers and see prophetically and be yielded to it.

00:04:02.346 --> 00:04:07.743
And so, it's been amazing to watch what he's done with this little girl.

00:04:07.744 --> 00:04:16.727
Braden is very techy and very smart like his mama. Diana is very smart, and they are able to do things that I can't do.

00:04:16.728 --> 00:04:22.004
So, it's very interesting how we all flow together with our giftings.

00:04:22.005 --> 00:04:27.234
Diana's really smart with finances and things like that, and Braden's smart with technological things.

00:04:27.235 --> 00:04:37.918
Paisley is still trying to figure out what God's called her to do, but I see more of a prayer mantle on her than any kid usually at her age.

00:04:37.919 --> 00:04:41.157
I've never seen it before. And I'm not bragging because she's my kid.

00:04:41.158 --> 00:04:46.098
You know, you'll go, "Well, yeah, of course you'd say that because that's your child."No, no, no.

00:04:46.099 --> 00:04:51.194
This is different. It's different. I know. And I'm one of those Simon Cowells.

00:04:51.195 --> 00:05:01.634
I'm not going to tell the person if their kid can't sing very well and they're in there auditioning for tryouts for singing, I'm going to say, "Honey, you just don't got it.

00:05:01.635 --> 00:05:09.437
It's okay. You can develop it or something through voice lessons."I'm just really blunt.

00:05:09.438 --> 00:05:18.096
And so, you know, that's why I believe that God's called me to go to certain places and rattle the places with the prophetic gifting inside of you.

00:05:18.097 --> 00:05:23.323
God calls you to stir churches; God calls you to stir the people.

00:05:23.324 --> 00:05:34.875
I have pastors from all around the world watch me and say, "Brandon, you're stirring us up to get us ready for the end times."My job is to rattle the cages, to yell from there.

00:05:34.876 --> 00:05:47.138
And I don't ever feel like I'm correcting; I'm just yelling through what the Lord is telling me to say to pastors, to churches, to ministries to warn you that he's coming.

00:05:47.139 --> 00:06:01.439
And we must give altar calls. We must get the lost saved. Even if you don't think anybody in your congregation is going to be saved that night, give people the opportunity to make a choice.

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:07.399
And God's going to hold us accountable for it. And I'm so thankful that we're seeing that now.

00:06:07.400 --> 00:06:14.246
We're seeing some fruit of that. We're seeing some fruit and some change, and we're seeing God move on some hearts.

00:06:14.247 --> 00:06:21.999
And it's wonderful to see the opportunity for the lost to give their heart to Jesus Christ.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:28.820
So, my heart is souls; my heart is a passion for souls. And we're seeing so many saved on this channel.

00:06:28.821 --> 00:06:36.638
It's amazing to see what the Lord is doing in these last days. Either we believe that he's coming or we don't.

00:06:36.639 --> 00:06:41.704
Either we believe that the coming of the Lord is at hand or we don't.

00:06:41.705 --> 00:06:53.999
And if we do believe it, there'll be urgency behind what we say and how we act. Some of us are growing more than others.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:07:01.119
Some of us are going through the birthing pains of ministry that we've never walked before. And that's me and Diana. We've never walked this before.

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:13.962
So, we try to find camaraderie in people sometimes, and maybe the Lord always said for us to stay to ourselves and we need to grow with our birthing pains a little bit more privately.

00:07:13.963 --> 00:07:28.216
But I'm going to tell you this, it's all been amazing what the Lord has done with us in the last two and a half years. And the Lord spoke to me today and he told me to tell you this.

00:07:28.217 --> 00:07:57.093
We were driving down the road and I was going to do some things with Diana, and I'm telling you, I was looking over at a tree as I was driving and I was in the spirit praying, and all of a sudden the Lord said, "I want to talk to you about what's coming as you see this shot that President Trump has in his hand right now."Do you see that?

00:07:57.094 --> 00:08:14.635
He's about to interject. He's about to administer into the economy. Is that what a doctor does? Yeah, inject into the economy.

00:08:14.636 --> 00:08:19.632
He's about to show up and show off in a way the Lord is in your finances.

00:08:19.633 --> 00:08:25.634
And he said, "There'll be many of you."I want you to hear what he said.

00:08:25.635 --> 00:09:05.173
He said, "There'll be many of you that have had the opportunity and you have listened and obeyed what he's told you to do, and you over—just in a short amount of time—will have the wealth of what we talked about in Deuteronomy 8: wells you didn't dig, houses you didn't furnish, blessing and increase beyond anything you can ever comprehend, imagine, or think is coming to you."And the Lord told me, 'Brandon, I'm telling you, I'm going to show you today.'As I was driving, he said, 'I'm going to show you today.

00:09:05.174 --> 00:09:29.756
I show you a lot of the warnings on the other side of the coin, but I am going to allow you to see the blessing side right now privately between me and you, and you can tell the people what's coming.'As I was looking over, I saw that big thing.

00:09:29.757 --> 00:09:50.954
I saw great financial stimulation coming to try to make a rally, to make things happy, to make people excited, and to pull people out of the funk of this 'sky is falling'mentality where everything is going to zero.

00:09:50.955 --> 00:09:57.679
The oil wells—everybody's freaking out—and war, war, war.

00:09:57.680 --> 00:10:17.039
I saw a stimulation coming where Trump had a battle plan of how to get the votes, since he is the president in November. I saw certain investments skyrocketing.

00:10:17.040 --> 00:10:33.190
I saw certain things starting to take off and the Lord said, 'This is...'I saw certain countries that have been dormant starting to come up, like Cuba and others, and I saw a blessing.

00:10:33.191 --> 00:10:42.262
People say, 'Well, Brandon, you said you saw the...'Yes, I see two sides. I see the fruit of stimulus; I see debt.

00:10:42.263 --> 00:10:56.159
I see what is happening to the American economy with a shot that only lasts for a little bit. It's like an adrenaline rush.

00:10:56.160 --> 00:11:19.039
Caffeine at Starbucks only lasts for a little bit, but it makes you feel good for probably two hours until you crash, but it still gets you through for that little time.

00:11:19.040 --> 00:11:30.639
I saw certain rug pulls happening with great manipulation, like it was with silver.

00:11:30.640 --> 00:11:36.891
What everybody said was not normal, what happened with silver. Remember it was way high and I told you?

00:11:36.892 --> 00:11:47.518
Everything I say on this is all in my opinion for your entertainment purposes only.

00:11:47.519 --> 00:11:54.178
I am not a financial adviser. I say all that because it's what I've been told to say.

00:11:54.179 --> 00:12:05.388
This is what our channel is about as the prophetic part of what I believe, but this is what I feel the Lord has told me and I'm entitled to my opinion.

00:12:05.389 --> 00:12:19.953
I believe this is what the Lord has told me. I could miss it; I could be off. I want to say, I saw... remember when I talked about silver?

00:12:19.954 --> 00:12:32.034
The Lord said, 'Today's a great day to sell silver,'and it was at a hundred and some dollars an ounce and then within just 24 hours it went down, but I wasn't allowed to talk about it.

00:12:32.034 --> 00:12:36.459
The Lord tells me things and he talks to me about investments.

00:12:36.460 --> 00:12:56.638
He tells me about property, he talks to me about all kinds of things and says, 'In the future, this will be worth this.'I'll just drive down the road and say, 'That right there is a good investment.'They are huge ideas, but I just pray over it.

00:12:56.639 --> 00:13:16.398
There are certain things that are coming. The Lord showed me about finances and the body of Christ, that there'll be rug pulls, great manipulation, and things to get you not to trust it—to trust banks and these other things—but then they'll try to get you to trust it.

00:13:16.399 --> 00:13:30.879
They don't want you to become really wealthy. I saw a manipulation where they don't want Bob, Joe, and Billy Bob to become extremely wealthy.

00:13:30.880 --> 00:13:43.757
So, if they're not smart enough to know when to hold them, know when to fold them, know when to walk away, and know when to run, you lose it all.

00:13:43.758 --> 00:13:50.771
And the Lord said, 'Count your money while you're sitting at the table.'I'm teasing; he didn't say that.

00:13:50.772 --> 00:14:00.459
I joke around with the Lord. The Lord has a great sense of humor.

00:14:00.460 --> 00:14:07.319
You all need to get to know him. Some of you do, but he has an amazing sense of humor.

00:14:07.320 --> 00:14:19.518
He made me, and so you have to go, 'If he can make me, he has a great sense of humor.'He likes to laugh and talk about sports.

00:14:19.519 --> 00:14:33.195
He likes to have fun. He loves his kids. Most people only see God as a religious fixture, like something too much to talk to or have a relationship with.

00:14:33.196 --> 00:14:40.196
But God is an ever-present help in a time of need. He loves you and he has a plan for your life.

00:14:40.197 --> 00:14:50.689
Most people only see him as someone you go to on Sunday or take communion and confess, then hope he forgives you.

00:14:50.690 --> 00:15:03.356
But I can assure you he does, and he has a plan for your life. I hear these things whenever he's talking to me about what's about to take place.

00:15:03.357 --> 00:15:09.721
I saw certain currencies going up in value. I saw a breakthrough in certain things.

00:15:09.722 --> 00:15:21.912
And he said, 'Remember I told you it wouldn't be as much as what people thought and they'll be disappointed in it, but it's a startup.'This is what you would call a startup if you listen to me.

00:15:21.913 --> 00:15:30.815
I saw Elon... I can say this because I saw Elon using something for X in the days ahead.

00:15:30.816 --> 00:15:37.037
I saw a lot of exchange and things about to take place even with Elon.

00:15:37.038 --> 00:15:54.799
I saw great, huge investments in certain cryptos from certain individuals like Michael Saylor and people like that who will dump billions into certain things in the days ahead.

00:15:54.800 --> 00:16:07.612
Hundreds of billions. Countries. I didn't see trillions; I saw hundreds of billions, and it was in certain countries and nations.

00:16:07.613 --> 00:16:28.453
I saw a frenzy that was coming in the future. I don't know when, but the Lord said specifically to pray for the summer months, to pray for this time frame with this shot.

00:16:28.454 --> 00:16:36.229
Praying for him to have wisdom on how to implement it. In my opinion, how will he implement this?

00:16:36.230 --> 00:16:45.395
I saw the man that takes over Jerome Powell's place trying to come up with a battle plan: 'How do we save America?

00:16:45.396 --> 00:16:56.754
How do we become what we need to be in these last days?'Basically, I don't know how else to say it.

00:16:56.755 --> 00:17:08.314
As I watched Putin, I saw a plan trying to take place concerning getting rid of Zelensky in the days ahead.

00:17:08.315 --> 00:17:16.740
'How do we eliminate Zelensky? How do we take him out?'Do you get what I'm saying?

00:17:16.741 --> 00:17:30.399
I saw the puppet Pinocchio with the big nose, Zelensky, who was being manipulated by Macron and the EU.

00:17:30.400 --> 00:17:43.279
He was a puppet, a marionette, and he was moving around. People say, 'Well, I like Zelensky.'You have to have more discernment.

00:17:43.280 --> 00:17:49.968
You have to come up higher in your prayer life. If you think these people are good, you are falsely mistaken.

00:17:49.969 --> 00:18:02.570
These people are not good. Am I saying Putin's good? No, he is not. They are all bad.

00:18:02.571 --> 00:18:16.479
But you can't let one go, 'Well, he's the good guy, he's the bad guy.'There are no good guys in politics.

00:18:16.480 --> 00:18:28.558
They may pretend they're good, but every one of them got there... you have to let the elevator go to the top.

00:18:28.559 --> 00:18:35.023
I'm telling you by the spirit of God what I've seen and the darkness in these nations in Europe.

00:18:35.024 --> 00:18:42.159
As the king was here—I don't know if he's still here or not—I told you he was a scorpion.

00:18:42.160 --> 00:18:50.365
And he came out with a scorpion and he turned towards Canada, he turned towards Europe, and he was getting ready to pinch his pincers.

00:18:50.366 --> 00:19:01.678
Then he comes here, has dinner, and does things. I told you I saw an antichrist darkness trying to overshadow our president.

00:19:01.679 --> 00:19:12.278
I didn't know that he was coming this week. That's when I saw it on Sunday and I said there's something very dark trying to come around Trump.

00:19:12.279 --> 00:19:24.719
What is this? I had no idea. It's the king. What is influencing Trump behind the scenes that we didn't know? What counsel was he being given from the king?

00:19:24.720 --> 00:19:31.869
Well, we're all trying to be friends and have fist bumps and eat pie and maybe some lemonade or whatever because we know Trump doesn't drink.

00:19:31.870 --> 00:19:38.541
But I saw an Antichrist spirit trying to be and I said, "What is this darkness, Lord?"And I couldn't get through it.

00:19:38.542 --> 00:19:42.818
And I thought, "What's going around Trump?"Then the king shows up.

00:19:42.819 --> 00:19:47.314
I said, "There's a darkness."Now, am I saying the antichrist is the king?

00:19:47.315 --> 00:19:53.553
No. But there is a demonic covering over the royals that is dark.

00:19:53.554 --> 00:20:00.230
And I'm telling you, I've seen this—the lizard people. I've said there's darkness there.

00:20:00.231 --> 00:20:06.239
And I said there's part there like this is lineages of lizard stuff.

00:20:06.240 --> 00:20:12.639
And I saw certain royal families that have been keeping the bloodline clean.

00:20:12.640 --> 00:20:19.203
I saw darkness. Am I wrong? I don't know. So I just tell you what I saw.

00:20:19.204 --> 00:20:25.108
You said, "Well, Brandon, you're drinking some bad Kool-Aid."Hey, I'm just telling you what I saw.

00:20:25.109 --> 00:20:32.884
And so when I saw him here, I thought that's what we saw. That's what the darkness was.

00:20:32.885 --> 00:20:38.682
Because I told Braden, I said, "What in the world was that? I haven't seen that darkness ever around Trump.

00:20:38.683 --> 00:20:52.733
What was over his shoulder talking to him?"I said, "I saw an antichrist demonic spirit talking to President Trump this week."And the Lord said, "Pray for him."And it was so heavy.

00:20:52.734 --> 00:20:56.714
The darkness was so heavy. I thought, "What is this? What did he yield to?

00:20:56.715 --> 00:21:02.239
Who's in there talking to him?"We talked about it for hours.

00:21:02.240 --> 00:21:11.999
I told Braden, "I have never seen this around our president ever."I was puzzled. I said, "What is talking on his right shoulder?

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:27.353
What is this influencing our president that looks like this?"And then this week happened and then he spoke to our Congress.

00:21:27.354 --> 00:21:37.480
He was invited to speak. So I thought, is this the darkness that you warned me about on Sunday as we're in Wednesday?

00:21:37.481 --> 00:21:45.519
Very interesting to me because I've never again, like I said, I've never seen that kind of darkness around our president before.

00:21:45.520 --> 00:21:50.250
Even when MBS shows up, I don't see it like that until that man showed up.

00:21:50.251 --> 00:21:59.170
And I thought that's interesting. So let's see what happens over the days ahead.

00:21:59.171 --> 00:22:05.970
As you look here, he is—all the Democrats are standing up front.

00:22:05.971 --> 00:22:15.816
Of course, that's their friend. Can you show him? Just a little bit.

00:22:15.817 --> 00:22:26.879
I wanted to show that he was there. So, he spoke to everybody.

00:22:26.880 --> 00:22:34.563
I didn't listen to the speech. I don't care to listen to the speech, so it is what it is.

00:22:34.564 --> 00:22:38.931
It's very interesting though. I just want you all to be watching.

00:22:38.932 --> 00:22:46.959
I told you a great acceleration of things would start to take place as of April 1st.

00:22:46.960 --> 00:22:52.138
And we are at the end of April on the 29th. Today—tomorrow is the last day of April.

00:22:52.139 --> 00:22:58.897
And look at all that is happening ever since then. It's been a very interesting couple of weeks, huh?

00:22:58.898 --> 00:23:16.152
All right. And then they put two kings. Is that his right shoulder?

00:23:16.153 --> 00:23:30.558
If he's facing that way, yes, on his right shoulder. There's a darkness on his right shoulder.

00:23:30.559 --> 00:23:38.744
It's very specific. Do you see the Lord tells me things very specifically?

00:23:38.745 --> 00:23:45.942
There will be a darkness on his right shoulder. And I said, "What am I looking at?"And I didn't know.

00:23:45.943 --> 00:23:54.914
And I told you, I said, "I'm looking into a two-state solution. I'm looking into MBS. I saw Jared. I saw these people.

00:23:54.915 --> 00:24:03.474
I saw Ezekiel 38 and 39."And I said, "We're rice paper thin for the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ."And many of you don't really realize it.

00:24:03.475 --> 00:24:10.639
There's not enough urgency in the body of Christ. Most churches aren't even giving altar calls.

00:24:10.640 --> 00:24:15.031
Do you understand? But there's no urgency in the body of Christ.

00:24:15.032 --> 00:24:23.747
If there is urgency, the Lord said, "Tell them I'm coming. Tell them I'm coming."So I do it every single time.

00:24:23.748 --> 00:24:35.569
I try to spur you, you know. Some people don't like it though and they think I'm challenging.

00:24:35.570 --> 00:24:42.693
I guess they send me the emails: "Grow up"or whatever. You don't have to listen.

00:24:42.694 --> 00:24:48.977
Turn it off. But at least I can say I warned you. Go ahead. Next.

00:24:48.978 --> 00:24:59.037
Do you have anything else on? Oh, yeah. And then he said he wants to stay.

00:24:59.038 --> 00:25:06.110
So Jerome Powell wants to keep his job. He wants to work it. I told you he'd be looking for employment.

00:25:06.111 --> 00:25:14.239
Nobody wants to hire him. He's looking for a job. I saw a help wanted sign; he wanted help.

00:25:14.240 --> 00:25:20.470
One of those help wanted signs. He was out there begging for work.

00:25:20.471 --> 00:25:27.033
But he's like, "I want to stay there."And I'm like, I'm sure Trump, the day he loses his position of where he's at right now, he's going to fire him.

00:25:27.034 --> 00:25:35.397
He can go sell ice cream with Joe Biden. You and Joe Biden can open an ice cream shop.

00:25:35.398 --> 00:25:47.100
But he's done. Very interesting. Too late. Powell wants to stay at the Fed because he can't get a job anywhere else.

00:25:47.101 --> 00:26:04.728
I told you he's going to be looking for work. I don't know. Powell says he will stay on as Fed governor after his term as chair ends.

00:26:04.729 --> 00:26:11.278
You're fired. Get out of here. You're fired. That's what he's going to tell him.

00:26:11.279 --> 00:26:14.527
I don't know if he can fire him, but I'm sure if he finds a way, he can.

00:26:14.528 --> 00:26:23.750
Trust me. You're fired. Get out of here. All right. Go ahead.

00:26:23.751 --> 00:26:27.965
Next. This one. What is that, baby? Okay, let's listen to this.

00:26:27.966 --> 00:26:44.188
I want you to hear this. What was said about the peaches in New Jersey? Okay.

00:26:44.189 --> 00:26:50.754
Now I am walking through the peach orchard at Heilig Orchards in Mullica Hill, New Jersey.

00:26:50.755 --> 00:26:59.673
200 acres surround weather swings during the last month or so. His crop here has been a total loss, complete devastation.

00:26:59.674 --> 00:27:06.459
Also, another important note, he tells me that he believes peaches are going to be almost impossible to come by in New Jersey.

00:27:06.460 --> 00:27:15.100
And if you do get them, they'll probably be much more expensive.

