02:27:22.640 --> 02:27:32.239
I give you everything. Your mercy is running after, is running after me.

02:27:32.240 --> 02:27:45.119
And all my life you have been faithful. And all my life you have been so, so good.

02:27:45.120 --> 02:27:56.079
With every breath that I am able, I'm going to sing of the goodness of God.

02:27:56.080 --> 02:28:04.799
I'm going to sing of the goodness of God. Thank you, Lord. We love y'all.

02:28:04.800 --> 02:28:19.479
Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much and we love you and we'll see you again. God bless y'all. Bye-bye.

